attributeList.attribute: INTerAction database (IntAct) provides an open source database and toolkit for the storage, presentation and analysis of molecular interactions.
European Bioinformatics Institute; Wellcome Trust Genome Campus; Hinxton, Cambridge; CB10 1SD; United Kingdom
A collection of literature-mined stable and functionally defined human molecular complexes of known stoichiometry and biological role.

names.alias: Clathrin assembly protein complex 3 beta large chain
Clathrin assembly protein large beta chain

attributeList.attribute: Probably acts in clathrin-independent traffic of membrane proteins from the Golgi apparatus to vacuoles.

By similarity to AP-1 (CPX-532), consists of a core complex with two appendages projecting from the large (L) subunits via flexible linkers which bind a variety of regulatory proteins which may contribute to substrate specificity.
